<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT23">
<l>vittu miṭalvēṇṭuṅ kollō viṭaiyaṭartta</l>
<l>patti yuḻavaṉ paḻampuṉattu moytteḻunta</l>
<l>kārmēka maṉṉa karumāl tirumēṉi</l>
<l>nīrvāṉaṅ kāṭṭu nikaḻntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is there a need [for us] to sow seeds in the ancient fields of</l>
<l>the bhakti Ploughman who subdued the bulls?</l>
<l>The passing water[-bearing] clouds is reminiscent of the sacred body of the dark Māl</l>
<l>who is like black clouds that rise in clusters.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
